cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is primarily focused on visual face tracking, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also extensively uses deep learning methods, which falls under the subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper proposes an end-to-end attentive deep learning based tracker, which involves attention mechanisms and feature selection, which are subfields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with video surveillance, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM) and computer security (cs.CR).
